=== Prompt Version Comparison ===

This script requires an LLM API key to run the full benchmark.
The V5 system prompt is defined as SYSTEM_PROMPT_V5 constant.

V5 prompt length: 1533 characters
V5 prompt lines: 34

Claimed results (from blog, require LLM API to verify):
Version              Accuracy    Parse   Tokens
------------------------------------------------
V1 Baseline               62%      70%     5100
V2 + Role                 91%      97%     2100
V3 + FewShot              94%      97%     2400
V4 + Structure            94%      99%     2200
V5 + Constraints          96%      99%     1680
